title: Maaike Aarts
text:
Maaike Aarts (born in Amsterdam on 10 March 1976) is a Dutch violinist. She is a member of the Royal Concertgebouw Orchestra, for which she plays as a first violin, since December 2004.
She was briefly a member of the heavy metal band Celestial Season, playing in their 1995 releases Solar Lovers and Sonic Orb.
